 Naramaro Rebellion|ja|橘奈良麻呂の乱|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tachibana no Naramaro Rebellion|qq=}}. * 758 CE (Tenpyō Hōji 2): Serving as Governor of [[:en:Yamato Province|Yamato Province]].
