User:Immanuelle/Senior Fifth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 正五位}} in May; promoted to {{ill|Jushi-i|ja|従四位下|lt=Junior Fourth Rank, Lower Grade|1=Junior Fourth Rank|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jushi-i|13=User:Immanuelle/Junior Fourth Rank|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 従四位}} in August for his role in suppressing the {{ill|Tachibana no Naramaro Rebellion|ja|橘奈良麻呂の乱|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tachibana no Naramaro Rebellion|qq=}}. * 758 CE (Tenpyō Hōji 2): Serving as Governor of [[:en:Yamato Province|Yamato Province]].
